Subject: Emailed report with files containing passwords
Description: I tried creating a report with files containing passwords. I must be missing something. In AIC I can see a server with a file containing a pwd. However in the report and in the results where I thought I should pull the info from, that file is not reported on. I added screenshots.
What_We_Know__c:
Today we:

Identified two views that provide the desired data for the Passwords report. This includes the OpenShares_SDDDetails and the FS_SharesRanked_SDD views. We then modified the current report to display 2 rows including both of these views. This will display two sets of information from both views in one report.
